_________________More Safe Browsing Tips_____________________________

Avoid pirated material on the web.

Take care when typing and watch out for typos in web addresses.

One of the best security habits you can have is to update software regularly. However, you will not be doing this for Chrome in order to keep your browser version the same as the one used in this activity.

Block or require websites to ask to access resources, such as using your camera, running scripts, disclosing your location, and displaying pop-ups.
